data.text:
Character Analysis of Mok : Persons with the name Mok, have a great deal of self-confidence and are therefore likely to achieve success. They are generally work-oriented Persons who have a plan for everything they do. They are disciplined and have a high standard of honesty, are dependable, serious-minded individuals who need to be practical about all that they do.

Love Life of Mok : Persons are voracious regarding intimate impulses & want to try everything and love freedom in all respects.

Name Letter Analysis of Mok

M : Persons are a workaholic! A high-energy workhorse, Persons don't need much sleep and are very healthyO : Persons know where the moral high ground is, and always try to take itK : Persons are all about enlightenment

Acoording to vedic astrology , Rashi for the name Mok is Simha or Sinh and Moon sign associated with the name Mok is Leo.

The name Mok has Fire element. Sun is the Ruling Planet for the name Mok . The name Mok having moon sign as Leo is represented by The Lion and considered as Fixed .

Normally, people with the name Mok keep their promises. They like to live a king size life. Such people stay in their limits and are fearless.

Other name options, having Leo moon sign are name starting with : Ma, Me, Mu, Mi, Mo, Ta, Ti, Tu, Te, To, Mr, Ta, Ts.
